{"word":"πλώιμος","slug":"πλώιμος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n84021\" key=\"plw/imos\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">πλώ-ῐμος</orth> or <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">πλόϊμος</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ον</itype>, (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">πλώω</etym>) <sense id=\"n84021.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">fit for sailing</tr_>: </sense> <sense n=\"1\" id=\"n84021.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> of a ship, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">seaworthy,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0003.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:29\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.29</biblScope></bibl>,<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0003.tlg001.perseus-grc1:50\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">50</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0003.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:13\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.13</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg056.perseus-grc1:23\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.\">D.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">56.23</biblScope></bibl>, etc.; also, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">fit for shipbuilding,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τῶν ξύλων τὰ -ώτατα</quote_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Plu.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.676a</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n84021.2\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> of navigation, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἤδη πλωϊμωτέρων ὄντων</foreign> as <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform