orm=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Str.\">Str.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.4.1</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"4\" id=\"n84021.4\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> of goods, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">sea-borne,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg2734.tlg013:163:2\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Just.\">Just.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">Nov.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">163.2</biblScope></bibl>.—Most codd. of <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></author> </bibl> and <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.\">D.</a></author> </bibl> give <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">πλόϊμος</foreign> (also found in Thphr.l.c.), though in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></author> </bibl> they give <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">πλωΐζω.</foreign> </sense> </entryFree>"}]}